msgctxt "an10.68:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.68:0.2"
msgid "7. Yamakavagga "
msgstr "7. Pairs "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.68:0.3"
msgid "68. Dutiyanaḷakapānasutta "
msgstr "68. At Naḷakapāna (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.68:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā naḷakapāne viharati palāsavane. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha stayed near Naḷakapāna in the parrot tree grove. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.68:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā tadahuposathe bhikkhusaṅghaparivuto nisinno hoti. "
msgstr "Now, at that time it was the sabbath, and the Buddha was sitting surrounded by the Saṅgha of monks. "

msgctxt "an10.68:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā bahudeva rattiṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassetvā samādapetvā samuttejetvā sampahaṃsetvā tuṇhībhūtaṃ tuṇhībhūtaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ anuviloketvā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ āmantesi: "
msgstr "The Buddha spent most of the night educating, encouraging, firing up, and inspiring the mendicants with a Dhamma talk. Then he looked around the Saṅgha of monks, who were so very silent. He addressed Venerable Sāriputta, "

#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.126, sc2
msgctxt "an10.68:2.1"
msgid "“Vigatathinamiddho kho, sāriputta, bhikkhusaṅgho. "
msgstr "“Sāriputta, the Saṅgha of mendicants is rid of dullness and drowsiness. "

msgctxt "an10.68:2.2"
msgid "Paṭibhātu taṃ, sāriputta, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammī kathā. "
msgstr "Give them some Dhamma talk as you feel inspired. "

msgctxt "an10.68:2.3"
msgid "Piṭṭhi me āgilāyati; "
msgstr "My back is sore, "

msgctxt "an10.68:2.4"
msgid "tamahaṃ āyamissāmī”ti. "
msgstr "I’ll stretch it.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.68:2.5"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho āyasmā sāriputto bhagavato paccassosi. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” Sāriputta replied. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an10.68:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā catugguṇaṃ saṅghāṭiṃ paññāpetvā dakkhiṇena passena sīhaseyyaṃ kappesi pāde pādaṃ accādhāya sato sampajāno uṭṭhānasaññaṃ manasi karitvā. "
msgstr "And then the Buddha spread out his outer robe folded in four and laid down in the lion’s posture—on the right side, placing one foot on top of the other—mindful and aware, and focused on the time of getting up. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.68:3.2"
msgid "Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "There Sāriputta addressed the mendicants: "

msgctxt "an10.68:3.3"
msgid "“āvuso bhikkhave”ti. "
msgstr "“Reverends, mendicants!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.68:3.4"
msgid "“Āvuso”ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato sāriputtassa paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Reverend,” they replied. "

msgctxt "an10.68:3.5"
msgid "Āyasmā sāriputto etadavoca: "
msgstr "Sāriputta said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an10.68:4.1"
msgid "“Yassa kassaci, āvuso, saddhā natthi kusalesu dhammesu, hirī natthi … "
msgstr "“Reverends, whoever has no faith, conscience, prudence, energy, and wisdom; who doesn’t want to listen, doesn’t memorize the teachings, examine their meaning, or practice accordingly, and is not diligent when it comes to skillful qualities "

msgctxt "an10.68:4.2"
msgid "ottappaṃ natthi … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.68:4.3"
msgid "vīriyaṃ natthi … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.68:4.4"
msgid "paññā natthi … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.68:4.5"
msgid "sotāvadhānaṃ natthi … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.68:4.6"
msgid "dhammadhāraṇā natthi … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.68:4.7"
msgid "atthūpaparikkhā natthi … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.68:4.8"
msgid "dhammānudhammappaṭipatti natthi … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.68:4.9"
msgid "appamādo natthi kusalesu dhammesu, tassa yā ratti vā divaso vā āgacchati, hāniyeva pāṭikaṅkhā kusalesu dhammesu no vuddhi. "
msgstr "can expect decline, not growth, in skillful qualities, whether by day or by night. "

msgctxt "an10.68:4.10"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, āvuso, kāḷapakkhe candassa yā ratti vā divaso vā āgacchati, hāyateva vaṇṇena hāyati maṇḍalena hāyati ābhāya hāyati ārohapariṇāhena; "
msgstr "It’s like the moon in the waning fortnight. Whether by day or by night, its beauty, roundness, light, and diameter and circumference only decline. "

